OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FOver half the Lake District's 18
OL,7,Fmillion annual visitors are domestic
OL,8,Ftourists, travelling from where they
OL,9,Flive in another part of the UK. Yet
OL,10,Fthe latest Visit Britain report has
OL,11,Ffound Domestic tourism has fallen in
OL,12,Fthe last year.
OL,14,FThe national tourism body warns the
OL,15,Fnumber of overnight trips UK visitors
OL,16,Fplan to make to other UK destinations
OL,17,Fis back to the level seen in March,
OL,18,Ffollowing the outbreak of conflict in
OL,19,Fthe Middle East.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
