OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FTwo of the top three factors putting
OL,7,Fpeople off traveling in the UK with an
OL,8,Fovernight stay in the next six months
OL,9,Fwere financial:
OL,11,FIn June, in one of his last acts as
OL,12,FPrime Minister, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fintroduced the Great British Summer
OL,14,FSavings Scheme.
OL,16,FThe scheme cut VAT on children's
OL,17,Fmeals, tourist attractions and culture
OL,18,Fand entertainment from 20% to 5% for
OL,19,Fthe duration of the school summer
OL,20,Fholidays.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FIt was hoped it would give parents and
OL,7,Fhospitality businesses a boost by
OL,8,Fencouraging families to make more
OL,9,Ftrips out around the UK.
OL,11,FHowever, businesses in the Lake
OL,12,FDistrict have been telling ITV Border
OL,13,Fthe same story: none of their
OL,14,Fcustomers seem to have heard about it.
OL,15,FThe sunshine, they say, is attracting
OL,16,Fvisitors to the Lake District, not the
OL,17,Fprice drop.
OL,19,FWatch Ryan Dollard's report:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FOne visitor in Bowness-on-Windermere
OL,7,Ftold ITV Border: "To be honest, we
OL,8,Fdidn't know anything about it until
OL,9,Fwe've walked in and saw the price on
OL,10,Fthe wall. When we saw about the VAT
OL,11,Fbeing reduced we thought yeah we'll
OL,12,Fcome in."
OL,14,FAt the World of Beatrix Potter
OL,15,Fattraction it was a similar story, but
OL,16,Fstaff were grateful it had brought
OL,17,Fprices down.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FSarah Melhuish, from the attraction
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think the tax break is
OL,8,Fabsolutely brilliant for tourism in
OL,9,FCumbria. Tourism is our lifeblood. We
OL,10,Frely on tourists here and especially a
OL,11,Flot of family visitors here, but it
OL,12,Fperhaps hasn't been as widely
OL,13,Fpublicised as it might be, although we
OL,14,Fare shouting about it a lot."
OL,16,FThe Lakeland Motor Museum says their
OL,17,Fcustomers are thrilled to learn their
OL,18,Fprices are cheaper, but it isn't the
OL,19,Fsaving scheme driving them through the
OL,20,Fdoors.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FChris Lowe from the museum says:
OL,7,F"About 10% of our customers walk in
OL,8,Fknowing there's a price decrease. So a
OL,9,Ffew know.
OL,11,F"But I think it's a happy surprise for
OL,12,Fthose with the funds to fill a car
OL,13,Fwith a tank of fuel and travel to the
OL,14,FLake District and enjoy a day out.
OL,16,F"So yeah, hopefully if we get the
OL,17,Fmessage out a bit more, people can use
OL,18,Fthe cheaper bus fares and the cheaper
OL,19,Fentry fee."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
