CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FThe Lake District's hospitality
OL,7,Fbusinesses have been calling for more
OL,8,Fsupport for years, as visitor numbers
OL,9,Fand spend has been consistently down
OL,10,Fsince the Covid19 Pandemic.
OL,12,FIn Cumbria Tourism's latest figures,
OL,13,F2024 saw a fall in both visitor
OL,14,Fnumbers, which were down 3.3% and the
OL,15,Fnumber of days they spent in the area,
OL,16,Fdown 5%.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
