OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FThe result was also a 5.7% drop in
OL,7,Frevenue, after adjustment for
OL,8,Finflation. That matters because the
OL,9,Fsame report also found tourism
OL,10,Fcontributed #4.6billion to the local
OL,11,Feconomy in 2024, supporting 74,823
OL,12,Fjobs, which equates to 28% of the
OL,13,Fcounty's workforce.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
