OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784726325
OL,3,CBrits are holidaying less in the UK,
OL,4,Clatest figures show
OL,6,FThat report found the number of
OL,7,Fvisitors staying overnight remained
OL,8,Fstable but the general trend was for
OL,9,Fshorter trips, with the number of
OL,10,Fnights visitors stayed dropping by
OL,11,F6.3%, which, similar to the latest
OL,12,FVisit Britain report, was thought to
OL,13,Fbe caused by rising prices and tighter
OL,14,Fpersonal finances.
OL,16,FThe vast majority of day visitors are
OL,17,Ffrom the North West of England and day
OL,18,Fvisitors fell by 4%, but the number
OL,19,Fhas dropped 18% since 2019.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
